message: Hello Bob, I'm excited to present you with our premium product, which holds significant value for you at $12000. To make this opportunity even more enticing, I am offering it to you at an exclusive price of $11000. This is a special deal tailored to recognize your interest and commitment. Don't miss out on this chance to secure a valuable asset at a highly favorable rate. Let's discuss further if this aligns with your financial plans and needs.
